00B4A5  1               ; ADD_R2_A
00B4A5  1               ; Add unsigned byte in A to 16-bit register R2.
00B4A5  1               ;
00B4A5  1               ; Returns:
00B4A5  1               ;   C = 1 only if 16-bit wrap occurred ($FFFF -> $0000)
00B4A5  1               ;   C = 0 otherwise
